description:
Sweet Eastside one bedroom home with a private outdoor patio off the eat-in-kitchen, gleaming hardwood floors and newly renovated shower - private storage + private laundry in the basement. Just a five minute walk to ALL the restaurants and shops on East Broadway. Available September 15th!

Owner pays for water/sewer, tenant pays for gas and electric.
